%h1
  Listing Roles

Intended as a reference and quick-view of member assignments.  You cannot directly modify roles.

.table-responsive
  %table.table.table-striped.table-condensed
    %thead
      %tr
        %th Code
        %th Title
        %th Description
        %th Cast?
        %th Crew?
        %th Sched?
        %th Members

    %tbody
      - @roles.each do |role|
        %tr
          %td= role.code
          %td= role.title
          %td= role.desc
          %td= role.cast ? 'Yes' : 'No'
          %td= role.crew ? 'Yes' : 'No'
          %td= role.schedule ? 'Yes' : 'No'
          %th
            %ul.list-unstyled
              - role.members.by_name.each do |member|
                %li= link_to_member member
